// Run: ./gradlew run --args="examples/woof/rebuild-if-while.woof"

labrador
my labrador has 3 toys

when she has more than 2 toys then
    she woofs "Plenty."
    she misplaces a toy
otherwise when she has 1 toy then
    she woofs "Just one."
otherwise
    she woofs "None."
bury

while she has more than 0 toys then
    she woofs "Still going."
    she misplaces a toy
bury
